Class AlgorithmNodeImp

  • java.lang.Object
    • implementations.algorithm.AlgorithmNodeImp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AlgorithmNode

    public class AlgorithmNodeImp
extends java.lang.Object
implements AlgorithmNode
    This class stores a representation of a node and core from the algorithm class. This allows us to check for validity and calculate time to run without extra baggage of the node class.
